      • Manager

        public Manager(java.lang.String managerName,
               java.lang.Integer teamWorth,
               java.lang.Integer place,
               java.lang.String communityName)
        Constructor
        Parameters:
        managerName - the name of the manager (should be the name of the User, who owns him.
        teamWorth - the worth of the team, which is owned by this manager
        place - the place in the community
        communityName - the name of the community, in which this manager plays.

      • Manager

        Parameters:
        managerJSON - the JSONObject with all necessary information
        communityName - the name of the Community, in which this manager should play.
